title: OTraki Rainbow Skipping Rope Kids, Adjustable Skipping Ropes for Kids, Wooden Handle Skipping Rope for Girls/Boys, Exercise Jump Rope Kid
features: 【Ideal Kids Skipping Rope】: Rainbow skipping rope is a mesmerizing color for boys and girls. It is specially designed for Children age 4-16 and even adult. Length: 2.5m/8.5FT. The combination of Blue handle and colorful rope is a cheerful color, and children will have fun doing exercises every day.

【Natural Material】: The round handles made of 100% natural pine wood is specially designed for peoples' palm curvature, easy to hold firmly and not easy to slip out of palm. Environmentally friendly paint protects the handle to the greatest extent, and the kids skipping rope has a built-in rubber band, which is highly elastic and not easy to knot or twist.

【Durable & Adjustable】: The rainbow jump rope adds a 15cm transparent rubber tube to the outside to minimize friction with the ground, making it more durable and wear-resistant. The length of the child skipping rope is easy to adjust, and the most suitable length can be adjusted according to different heights.

【Exercise】: Rope skipping can speed up blood circulation and improve cardiopulmonary and respiratory functions, improve immunity, promote stomach and digestive tract, and maintain health. In the process of playing with other children, it can effectively cultivate the spirit of unity and cooperation and enhance interpersonal skills.

【Ideal Gift】: OTraki kids skipping rope is not only a cute toy, but also a tool for exercise, suitable for children to enjoy the fun of jumping sports. Suitable for schools, companies, home entertainment and more. Great gift for kids on Children's Day, birthday, school and other festivals.
